attributes.Transcription: Hello, thank you for agreeing to take part of our study. In front of you, you will see a GoPro, we'll be using it for this task.
You please first change the battery within the GoPro camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the GoPro's battery.

attributes.Transcription: Thank you.
Next please change the SD card within the GoPro camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges their Sd card for the GoPro's.

attributes.Transcription: You might find it helpful to remove the battery.
Next, please turn on the GoPro camera by using the button on the side.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns on their GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Thank you.
Next, please turn off the GoPro camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns off their GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: To turn off the GoPro camera, please long press the button on the side.
Thank you.
Next, put this mount, the mount strap.

attributes.Action sentence: The student attaches the GoPro to the strap.

attributes.Transcription: Please put on a strap, on the strap mounting.
Please make sure the holes on the GoPro and on the strap are lined up before inserting the screw.
Thank you.
Next, please remove the shoulder strap and put on the tripod mount.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the GoPro from the strap.
The student places the GoPro on the tripod.

attributes.Transcription: Thank you.
Next, please remove the tripod mount and put on the hand mount.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the GoPro from the tripod.
The student places the GoPro on the handheld grip.

attributes.Transcription: Please push the GoPro into the hand mount and make sure the holes of the GoPro and the hand mount are aligned.
Thank you.
Lastly, please remove the hand mount from the GoPro and rest both on the table.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the GoPro from the handheld grip.

attributes.Transcription: Thank you very much.
That concludes everything for this task. Please go ahead and click the stop button.
